  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Site Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>· Assist Site Manager to supervise constructions work to ensure that quality works are produced &amp; all operations are carried out safely.</p>\n<p>· Ensure that correct construction drawings are used.</p>\n<p>· Ensure safe work procedures are implemented to control risk.</p>\n<p>· Familiar with relevant legal requirement.</p>\n<p>· Carry out day-to-day site operations and supervise a team of construction workers.</p>\n<p>· Carry out inspection as well as resolving and monitoring rectification works.</p>\n<p>· Assist and support Engineers in carrying out works as assigned.</p>\n<p>· Supervise the construction of works and incorporation of materials and ensure that they are carried out in accordance with the project plan.</p>\n<p>· Assist the engineers in ensuring that the works are carried out to schedule and in accordance with relevant regulations.</p>\n<p>· Ensure company’s safety rules are observed and obeyed.</p>\n<p>· Ensure safety measures are met on site.</p>\n<p>· Ad hoc assignments.</p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<p>· Minimum 3 years’ experience as a Site Supervisor in the Construction industry required.</p>\n<p>· At least Degree in Building/Civil Engineering or equivalent.</p>\n<p>· Strong communication skills with workers and subcontractors .</p>\n<p>· Preferably experience in Metal work structural.</p>",
